<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，一只狐狸在井边玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他在湿滑的石头上摔倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他掉进了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！我现在有大麻烦了。我怎么才能出去？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸想啊想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他找不到爬出井的办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试着在井底堆石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是它们很重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久，狐狸变得很悲观。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有办法出去。我会死在这儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，一只傻山羊停下来喝水，让狐狸看到了希望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，上边的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好。你在下面做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸很聪明。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上有了主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他回答，“我在喝水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那儿的水好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好！那是相当好！清凉。新鲜。干净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是我喝过最好的水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山羊真的很想喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些水看起来很好喝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能喝点水吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么才能喝到水呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很简单。跳进来就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，来了。小心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山羊太渴了，来不及多想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳进了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>渴极了的山羊喝呀喝呀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山羊很乐意待在井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸很高兴，因为他的计划正在完美地实施着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水很不错。现在，我不渴了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，山羊先生。我们现在有麻烦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么麻烦？我没看出有麻烦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们出不去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！我们该怎么办？我们会死在这里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冷静点儿。我有一个办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把你的前腿伸直，向上趴在墙上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，我就可以从你的背上跳起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，别担心！我随后会帮你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。好主意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸够到了井上边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他跳到了井外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他准备逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这傻子。我帮不了你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你答应过……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这你可不能怪我。你不该跳进井里的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下次，跳之前好好儿看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狡猾的狐狸转身跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>傻山羊孤独一人被困在井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为自己的愚蠢感到后悔，但是已经太晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>